trans-unit.source: Specifies the default names for the models in the [!INCLUDE[adonet_ef](~/add/includes/adonet-ef-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: For more information about the models in the [!INCLUDE[adonet_ef](~/add/includes/adonet-ef-md.md)], see [Metadata Workspace Overview](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/b9c75c95-7626-484d-86bb-2ddd4c7042e2).
trans-unit.target: Voor meer informatie over de modellen in de [!INCLUDE[adonet_ef](~/add/includes/adonet-ef-md.md)], Zie [metagegevens werkruimte overzicht](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/b9c75c95-7626-484d-86bb-2ddd4c7042e2).

trans-unit.source: Represents the default name for the conceptual model.

trans-unit.source: Represents the default name for the mapping between the conceptual model and the storage model.

trans-unit.source: Represents the default name for the mapping between the object model and the conceptual model.

trans-unit.source: Represents the default name for the object model.
